body_html:
Hi,

Thanks for the patch, but I don't think we can take this one.

This is part of the effort to get the docs updated ahead of moving the canned estimators out of tf.contrib.learn into tf.estimators.

The current version is consistent with the behavior of tf.estimator.Estimator.

The 1.2 docs and examples work, but master is always a work in progress.

Thanks Again.

body:
Hi,

Thanks for the patch, but I don't think we can take this one.

This is part of the effort to get the docs updated *ahead* of moving the canned estimators out of `tf.contrib.learn` into `tf.estimators`. 

The current version is consistent with the behavior of `tf.estimator.Estimator`.

The 1.2 docs and examples work, but `master` is always a work in progress.

Thanks Again.
